ZH: 请留意校园内的启事，以便及时了解最新消息。
EN: Please pay attention to the notices on campus to stay informed of the latest news.

ZH: 这是一则失物招领的启事，请帮忙寻找失主。
EN: This is a lost and found notice, please help find the owner.

ZH: 我们在校门口张贴了一则招聘启事，欢迎有意者前来应聘。
EN: We have posted a job notice at the school gate, welcome to come for an interview if interested.

ZH: 请勿随意摘花，校园已贴有相关启事。
EN: Please do not pick flowers without permission, notices have been posted on campus.

ZH: 新学期的课程信息已经在启事板上发布。
EN: The course information for the new semester has been posted on the notice board.

ZH: 我们急需志愿者，有意者请看启事上的联系方式。
EN: We are in urgent need of volunteers, please see the contact information on the notice.

ZH: 各位同学，请注意宿舍楼道内的火灾预防启事。
EN: Students, please pay attention to the fire prevention notices in the dormitory corridors.

ZH: 这是一则校园宣传启事，号召大家参加环保活动。
EN: This is a campus publicity notice, calling for everyone to participate in environmental activities.

ZH: 学校体育馆即将举办运动会，详细信息请看启事。
EN: The school gymnasium will hold a sports meeting, please refer to the notice for details.

ZH: 请勿在树上乱扔垃圾，校园已贴有相关启事。
EN: Please do not litter on trees, notices have been posted on campus.

ZH: 室友会议的时间地点已在启事上公布，请准时参加。
EN: The time and place of the roommate meeting have been announced on the notice, please attend on time.

ZH: 今日放学后进行紧急疏散演练，请认真遵守启事上的指示。
EN: An emergency evacuation drill will be conducted after school today, please follow the instructions on the notice carefully.

ZH: 请在车站的启事栏查看最新的班车时刻表。
EN: Please check the latest shuttle schedule on the notice board at the station.

ZH: 请在启事板上查看图书馆的闭馆通知。
EN: Please check the library's closing notice on the bulletin board.

ZH: 班级将进行爱国主义教育，详细安排请看启事。
EN: The class will carry out patriotic education, please refer to the notice for details.

ZH: 我们将在周五举办校园清洁日，请查看启事报名参与。
EN: We will hold a campus clean-up day on Friday, please check the notice to sign up for participation.

ZH: 请注意宿舍定期检查的启事，确保宿舍内的安全。
EN: Please pay attention to the notice of the regular inspection of the dormitory to ensure safety.

ZH: 学习小组的成员请按时参加周一的会议，启事已公布。
EN: Members of the study group please attend the meeting on Monday on time, the notice has been posted.

ZH: 请在宿舍门口的启事栏查看宿舍调整通知。
EN: Please check the dormitory adjustment notice on the notice board at the dormitory entrance.
